Class AuditConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.odk.collect.android.formentry.audit.AuditConfig

  • public class AuditConfig
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible for storing the current audit configuration, which contains three parameters: locationPriority, locationMinInterval and locationMaxAge.
